psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher

Interface ProteinEnricher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InteractorEnricher<Protein>, MIEnricher<Protein>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FullProteinEnricher, FullProteinUpdater, MinimalProteinEnricher, MinimalProteinUpdater

    public interface ProteinEnricher
extends InteractorEnricher<Protein>
    The Protein enricher is an enricher which can enrich either single protein or a collection. A protein enricher must be initiated with a protein fetcher. Sub enrichers: CvTerm, Organism. Additionally, the protein enricher has a protein remapper for finding dead or demerged proteins.
    Since:
    16/05/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
